<div id="index-banner" class="parallax-container">
	<div class="section no-pad-bot">
		<div class="container">
			<br><br>
			<h1 class="header center">Krewe</h1>
			<div class="row center">
				<h5 class="header col s12 light">The best way to form your social network</h5>
			</div>
			<div class="row center">
				<% if current_user %>
					<%= link_to "Home", user_path(current_user), class: "modal-trigger", class: 'btn-large waves-effect blue' %>
				<% else %>
					<%= link_to "Sign Up For Beta", beta_signup_path, class: "modal-trigger",  class: 'btn-large waves-effect blue' %>
				<% end %>
			</div>
			<br><br>

		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="parallax"><%= video_tag 'Diner.mp4', autoplay: true, loop: true, muted: true %></div>
</div>


<div class="container">
	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col s12 center">
				<%= image_tag "symbol" %>
				<p class="left-align light">Making friends as an adult is hard. In our youth, we had classes, sports teams, fraternities and sororities, and a bunch of other organizations that made it easy to form lasting bonds with other people. But once we leave campus and move away from our friends to find jobs, we don't have access to anything quite like those things to help us form a strong social group. Krewe fills that void to help you effortlessly build a powerful network that you can rely on to have amazing experiences and advance your career.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>


<div class="parallax-container valign-wrapper">
	<div class="parallax"><%= image_tag "people" %></div>
</div>

<div class="container">
	<div class="section">

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col s12 m4">
				<div class="icon-block">
					<h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">group</i></h2>
					<h5 class="center">Krewe connects you with a group of people</h5>

					<p class="light">No more profiles to browse through and superficial judgements. No swiping like your everyday dating app. You just start off with a group of at most six people. We want you to feel as comfortable as possible and we belive that being in a small group will make that possible. </p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col s12 m4">
				<div class="icon-block">
					<h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">my_location</i></h2>
					<h5 class="center">Everyone lives in your neighborhood</h5>

					<p class="light">We get that you're busy. Therefore, we only connect you with people who live close by so that going to hang out with them is not a big ordeal. With Krewe, getting together after a busy work day at a local bar or coffee shop is easy as everyone is within walking distance.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col s12 m4">
				<div class="icon-block">
					<h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">insert_invitation</i></h2>
					<h5 class="center">Meeting up is easy</h5>

					<p class="light">We provide you with the tools to make it really easy to set up events to do and get everyone involved. Doing things over and over again with your group is simple and fun, helping your form strong bonds and connections.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
</div>


<div class="parallax-container valign-wrapper">
	<div class="parallax"><%= video_tag 'beers.mp4', autoplay: true, loop: true, muted: true %></div>
</div>

